short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AI Data Scientist for all your Analytics Apps

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
MinusX is an Open Source AI data scientist that helps you use your existing analytics tools. When you install the chrome extension and navigate to a supported app (Eg: Jupyter Notebooks, Metabase, or Google Sheets), the extension adds a side panel chat to the app. Given an instruction, our agent operates your app to analyze data and answer queries.

Github: https://github.com/minusxai/minusx
Website: https://minusx.ai
